thread.title: Lyn Fryer
thread.title_full: Temple & Webster reviewed by Lyn Fryer

author: Lyn Fryer
title: Lyn Fryer
text:
I love the ambience that the Tiffany lamps bring to the different rooms in the home and guests ask whether they were bought overseas in some exotic, romantic location. Hopefully, they should be placing their individual orders if these timelessly elegant and beautiful lamps are still available!
I am thrilled to have these classic pieces in my home.
